Pull and Push Model:-

Pull Model:    Chef, Puppet (agent needed)
Push Model:    Ansible, Salt (no agent)

Install Ansible on Ubuntu:-
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install software-properties-common
sudo apt-add-repository ppa:ansible/ansible
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install ansible

########## Ansible Master Setup#######
sudo su -
adduser ansible
passwd ansible
visudo (for sudo access)    ansible   ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL
vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config (password authantication Yes)
su - ansible
ssh-keygen
ssh-copy-id hostname (hostname of node)


#########Ansible Node SetUP#######
sudo su -
adduser ansible
passwd ansible
visudo (for sudo access)    ansible   ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL
vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config (password authantication Yes)
su - ansible
ssh-keygen
ssh-copy-id hostname (hostname of node)
